Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl
    7     | TypedefDecl

    8 TypedefDecl: TYPEDEF VarType IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON
    9            | TYPEDEF STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON
   10            | TYPEDEF UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON

   11 FuncDecl: VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
   12         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

   13 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   14 VarDecl: VarType VarList SEMICOLON

   15 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   16 VarType: _VarType
   17        | CONST _VarType

   18 _VarType: BuiltinType
   19         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   20         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER
   21         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   22         | UNION IDENTIFIER
   23         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   24         | ENUM IDENTIFIER
   25         | _VarType ASTERISK
   26         | IDENTIFIER

   27 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   28        | VarInit
   29        | ε

   30 VarInit: IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList
   31        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN Expr
   32        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE InitList RBRACE
   33        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE RBRACE

   34 InitList: InitList COMMA InitItem
   35         | InitItem

   36 InitItem: Expr
   37         | LBRACE InitList RBRACE

   38 ArrayBoundList: ArrayBoundList ArrayBound
   39               | ArrayBound
   40               | ε

   41 ArrayBound: LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET
   42           | LBRACKET RBRACKET

   43 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   44          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   45          | Param
   46          | ELLIPSES
   47          | ε

   48 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   49      | VarType

   50 BuiltinType: CHAR
   51            | SHORT
   52            | INT
   53            | LONG
   54            | UNSIGNED
   55            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   56            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   57            | UNSIGNED INT
   58            | UNSIGNED LONG
   59            | FLOAT
   60            | DOUBLE
   61            | BOOL
   62            | VOID

   63 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   64           | ε

   65 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   66          | SEMICOLON

   67 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   68           | IDENTIFIER
   69           | ε

   70 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   71         | Enum
   72         | ε

   73 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   74     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   75 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   76      | ε

   77 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   78     | IfStmt
   79     | SwitchStmt
   80     | ForStmt
   81     | DoStmt
   82     | WhileStmt
   83     | ContinueStmt
   84     | BreakStmt
   85     | ReturnStmt
   86     | Block
   87     | TypeDecl
   88     | VarDecl
   89     | SEMICOLON

   90 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   91       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   92 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   93 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   94             | ε

   95 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   96         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

   97 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   98        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   99        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

  100 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

  101 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

  102 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

  103 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

  104 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
